snippet: Robert Karlsson moved into a tie for fourth at the Wells Fargo Championship, two shots behind the co-leaders Phil Mickelson and Nick Watney.
abstract: Robert Karlsson, golfer who has publicly battled nerves, moves into tie for fourth at Wells Fargo Championship, two shots behind co-leaders Phil Mickelson and Nick Watney.
lead_paragraph: Robert Karlsson moved into a tie for fourth at the Wells Fargo Championship, two shots behind the co-leaders Phil Mickelson and Nick Watney.

headline.seo: Robert Karlsson in Tie for Fourth at Wells Fargo Championship
headline.main: Winning Battle of Nerves Against Himself, a Player Takes On the Tour
headline.print_headline: Winning Battle of Nerves Against Himself, a Player Is Again Taking On the Tour
